  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Community Forestry in the Departments of Caquet  and Guaviare, towards the sustainable management of forests in the Colombian Amazon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to contribute to the sustainable management of forests and the reduction of deforestation in the area of influence of the Chiribiquete National Park in the Amazonian Region of Colombia. The initiative will support local peasant communities in the implementation of small community forestry and tourism projects. FCDS will promote the development of legal, market and technical conditions with local institutions, to favour the implementation of instruments such as agreements, contracts, concessions, associations or others to favour sustainable forest management with community organizations.</narrative>
  </description>
